description: The N|Solid Console is the default centralized system for communication with, diagnostics and remote control of applications running on the N|Solid Runtime. Combined, the N|Solid Platform intends to provide the most performant, optimizable, secure and professionally supported Node.js runtime, for highly scalable product deployments.
